#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>In such situation, feel free to experiment with this database and "
"then to create a new one for your own usage.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Du er velkommen til at eksperimentere i sådanne situationer og "
"oprette en ny til egen anvendelse.</strong>"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Requesting a document</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Anmode om et dokument</strong>"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Setting up the project folder email alias</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Konfigurér e-mail-alias for projektmappen</strong>"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A crucial part of business is as well making sure it is profitable. Odoo "
"helps you following up project profitability with the project Dashboard."
msgstr ""
"En central del af forretningen er at bevare rentabiliteten. Odoo gør det "
"muligt at følge projektøkonomien direkte i projektdashboardet."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A crucial part of the business is to transform prospects into customers, "
"then to follow up efficiently on the mission and finally to bill customers "
"in for your work. We got you covered all along this journey!"
msgstr ""
"En central del af forretningen er at omdanne interesserede til kunder, følge "
"op på ordrer effektivt og til sidst fakturere for dit arbejde. Vi hjælper "
"dig hvert skridt på vejen!"

