msgstr "Skabelon/bogføring – månedlig moms"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Accounting Firm package does not include any customization. Note that "
"<strong>Studio App </strong>would enable you to setup specific fields for "
"more robustness as well as much more advanced workflows and automations!"
msgstr ""
"Bogføringspakken indeholder ingen individuelle tilpasninger. Med <strong>"
"Studio-appen</strong> kan du tilføje specifikke felter samt udvide "
"arbejdsgange og automatiseringer for større fleksibilitet!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Accounting Firm package is of great help but may not cover all your needs...<br/>\n"
"            Fortunately, Odoo got you covered:"
msgstr ""
"Pakken til regnskabsfirmaer er nyttig, men dækker måske ikke alle dine behov "
"...<br/>\n"
"            Heldigvis giver Odoo dig den nødvendige støtte:"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Customer onboarding task contains details about actions to take to have "
"your customer in order."
msgstr ""
"Opgaven \"Onboarding af kunde\" indeholder oplysninger om de tiltag, der "
"skal gennemføres for at informere dine kunder."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The documents sent to the email alias of this project will arrive in the "
"root folder of the project. This can be considered as an inbox while sub "
"folders contain treated documents in an organized fashion."
msgstr ""
"Dokumenter, der sendes til projektets e-mailalias, gemmes i projektets "
"rodmappe, som fungerer som en indbakke. Undermapperne organiserer de "
"behandlede dokumenter."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "The project creation created as well some tasks to handle from now on."
msgstr ""
"Ved oprettelse af projektet blev der også genereret opgaver, som skal "
"udføres med det samme."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This creates an empty document in your project to be filled by your customer"
" by uploading a file from the email they receive. You could do so for all "
"required documents by the task."
msgstr ""
"Dette opretter et tomt dokument i dit projekt, som kunden kan udfylde ved at "
"uploade en fil fra den modtagne e-mail. Du kan gentage processen for alle "
"dokumenter, der er nødvendige for opgaven."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Time management"
msgstr "Tidsstyring"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To assign the Project Manager, open the Project App and open the settings of"
" the project, clicking the three dots in the top right corner of the "
"corresponding tile."
msgstr ""
"For at tildele en projektleder skal du åbne Projektappen og gå til "
"projektindstillingerne ved at klikke på de tre prikker øverst til højre på "
"den relevante flise."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To request a document such as an ID card or a bank statement, click New and "
"then Request."
msgstr ""
"For at anmode om et dokument, f.eks. et ID-kort eller en kontoudskrift, skal "
"du klikke på \"Ny\" og derefter \"Anmodninger\"."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To setup the project folder email alias, display the project top bar and add"
" the Documents shortcut."
msgstr ""
"For at oprette e-mailaliasset til projektmappen skal du åbne "
"projektværktøjslinjen og tilføje genvejen \"Dokumenter\"."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:mail.activity.type,name:accounting_firm.mail_activity_ubo_update
#: model:mail.activity.type,summary:accounting_firm.mail_activity_ubo_update
msgid "UBO update"
msgstr "Opdatér reelle ejer"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:project.tags,name:accounting_firm.project_tags_3
msgid "Ultimate Beneficial Owners"
msgstr "Reelle ejere"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model:product.template,name:accounting_firm.product_product_6_product_template
msgid "Ultimate Beneficial Owners register (Pack)"
msgstr "Registrering af reelle ejere (pakke)"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Odoo Accounting Firm package! This guide will help you manage"
" your missions efficiently from opportunity management to billing, as well "
"as requesting documents."
msgstr ""
"Velkommen til Odoo-pakken til regnskabsfirmaer! Denne vejledning viser, "
"hvordan du effektivt administrerer opgaver – fra håndtering af "
"salgsmuligheder og fakturering til anmodning om dokumenter."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcoming prospects"
msgstr "Byd potentielle kunder velkommen"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you confirm a sale order, know that the duplicated project is defined in the product you sold. You can edit the project to adjust the list for customer onboarding actions or folder architecture so that you save\n"
"                    time in the future."
msgstr ""
"Når du bekræfter en salgsordre, skal du være opmærksom på, at det "
"tilknyttede projekt er oprettet ud fra det solgte produkt. Du kan redigere "
"projektet for at tilpasse kundeintroduktionskampagner eller mappestrukturen "
"og dermed spare\n"
"                    tid fremover."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Whether you performed some work for a fixed price or based on time sheets, "
"you can expense your customer for this."
msgstr ""
"Fakturér arbejdet til kunden, uanset om det er fast pris eller "
"tidsregistreret."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gennemgå din Odoo-opsætning med os eller udforske flere funktioner?"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Yet be aware that by default, any email sent to info@yourcompanyname.example.com will create a new lead in your CRM pipeline!<br/>\n"
"                    You can verify this by opening the CRM App, opening the sales teams from the Configuration menu, and opening the sales team you have."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk, at hver e-mail sendt til info@dinvirksomhed.e.ksempel.com som "
"standard opretter et nyt lead i CRM-pipelinen!<br/>\n"
"                    Du kan kontrollere dette ved at åbne CRM-appen, gå til "
"\"Salgsteams\" under \"Konfiguration\" og vælge det ønskede salgsteam."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well change view for the list view for example, and click the New"
" button to report some time."
msgstr ""
"Du kan f.eks. ændre visningen til listevisning og klikke på \"Ny\" for at "
"registrere arbejdstid."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well submit a letter of mission to be digitally signed with the "
"<strong>Sign app</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også sende en ordrebekræftelse med digital underskrift via "
"<strong>e-Signaturappen</strong>."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can preview the quote at this stage. This view is for your customer to "
"confirm the mission."
msgstr ""
"I denne fase kan du forhåndsvise tilbuddet for at bekræfte ordren over for "
"kunden."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can still do it by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr "Du kan fortsat gøre dette ved at opdatere din pakke via Apps."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have access in the project Dashboard to all related documents and can follow up on earnings and costs effortlessly.<br/>\n"
"                    Don't forget to update your employee costs, in the setting tab, to compute relevant costs."
msgstr ""
"I projektoversigten har du adgang til alle tilknyttede dokumenter og kan "
"nemt følge indtægter og udgifter.<br/>\n"
"                    Husk at opdatere personaleudgifterne i indstillingerne "
"for at beregne de relevante omkostninger."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just got a all and a customer wants to know more about your rates and "
"services. Rather than sending him an email on the side, leverage the "
"centralised chatter capability and most of all, do not lose this lead!"
msgstr ""
"Du har netop modtaget en forespørgsel, hvor kunden vil vide mere om dine "
"priser og tjenester. I stedet for at sende en separat e-mail kan du bruge "
"den centrale chatterfunktion og samtidig undgå at miste kunden!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just got a all and a customer wants you for the job, congratulations!"
msgstr ""
"Du har netop modtaget en ordre, og kunden ønsker at hyre dig til opgaven. "
"Tillykke!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might have tested the Accounting Firm package with or without demo data.<br/>\n"
"            In any case, you may have written records in journals which are not deletable and which might be an issue for your traceability."
msgstr ""
"Du har måske testet bogføringspakken med eller uden demodata.<br/>\n"
"I begge tilfælde kan der være journalposter, som ikke kan slettes, og som "
"kan påvirke sporbarheden."

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You might want to setup questionnaires to fine tune your quotations and "
"clarify the interactions with your customers. Have a look at the "
"<strong>Survey App</strong> to do so!"
msgstr ""
"Du kan oprette spørgeskemaer for at optimere tilbud og forbedre "
"kundedialogen. Tag et kig på <strong>Spørgeundersøgelser-appen</strong>!"

#. module: accounting_firm
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:accounting_firm.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Your Odoo Accounting Firm package includes essential apps to streamline your"
" operations:"
msgstr ""
"Din Odoo-pakke til regnskabsfirmaer indeholder alle centrale apps til at "
"effektivisere dine processer:"

